title: Chairman Schiff on CIA Interim Report on Anomalous Health Incidents
summary: “Over the past year, the Intelligence Committee has placed the highest priority on overseeing our response to the reports of anomalous health incidents by employees of the IC and other agencies. We owe those who serve our nation the highest-quality care, and the acknowledgment that they are heard and believed. “The interim report on the investigation into the cause of these incidents by the CIA is...
